data.description: Introducing a stunning home in one of San Antonio's most sought-after locations! This beautiful property is nestled near the medical center, Huebner Oaks, The Rim, and La Cantera, offering the convenience of nearby amenities and attractions. Situated in a gated community, this home provides both security and peace of mind.    Step inside to discover the newly installed vinyl flooring on the first floor, adding a touch of modern elegance. The kitchen and bathrooms showcase upgraded Quartz countertops, creating a sleek and stylish look. The entire home boasts new light fixtures, enhancing the ambiance and providing a fresh aesthetic.    Additional updates include a new garage door opener and bathroom mirrors, ensuring convenience and functionality. The HVAC system is only 2 years old, providing efficient and reliable climate control throughout the home.    One of the standout features of this property is its expansive backyard, one of the largest in the entire gated community. It's perfect for outdoor activities, entertaining guests, and creating lasting family memories.    This home is truly a must-see! Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a beautiful property in an exceptional location. Schedule a viewing and experience the charm and elegance of this remarkable home firsthand.
